The cross sections of monitor reaction were defined by

The tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target was used in
the generator. The effective source neutron energy at
irradiation position was determined by the Nb/Zr
method, and the uncertainty in the neutron energy at
around 3 cm was estimated to be 200 keV from a
consideration of the sample sizes, beam diameter of
about 3-4 mm, and the uncertainty in the Nb/Zr method.
